import { Box, Grid, Paper, TextField } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function BaseComponent() {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Paper>
                <form>
                <Grid container>
                        <Grid item md={6} xs={6}>
                        search field
                         <TextField 
                              variant="outlined" 
                              label="get a git user information" 
                              placeholder="search"
                              fullWidth />
                        </Grid>
                        <Grid item md={6} xs={6}>
                          
                        </Grid>
                </Grid>
                </form>
            </Paper>
        </Box>
    )
}
